| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3478 — Recovery Inhibition (alphalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cb5af4e9-4835-5fd3-9389-bab4a1ffd68f"
